      • extraListTo

        public List<String> extraListTo(String contextPath,
                                File dir,
                                Writer out,
                                String path,
                                List<DirectoryEntry> entries)
                         throws HistoryException,
                                IOException
        Write a HTML-ized listing of the given directory to the given destination.
        Parameters:
        contextPath - path used for link prefixes
        dir - the directory to list
        out - write destination
        path - virtual path of the directory (usually the path name of dir with the source root directory stripped off).
        entries - basenames of potential children of the directory to list. Gets filtered by IgnoredNames.
        Returns:
        a possible empty list of README files included in the written listing.
        Throws:
        HistoryException - when we cannot get result from SCM
        IOException - when any I/O problem
        NullPointerException - if a parameter except files is null
